      <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-rust">Case Studies</span>
      <h1 class="display-xl cs-hero__title">Real scenarios.<br/>Real closings.</h1>
      <p class="lede cs-hero__lede">Every borrower's situation is different. These are real financing scenarios — the complex, the time-sensitive, the "another lender said no" — and how we structured a path to closing. Educational examples, anonymized.</p>
      <div class="cs-search"><input type="search" id="csSearch" placeholder="Search by loan type, scenario…" aria-label="Search case studies" autocomplete="off" /></div>
    </div>
  </header>

